| 1 | Fix Names in a Table | Easy | [▶ Practice](sql_sandbox.html?slug=fix-names-in-a-table) |
| 2 | Find Users With Valid E-Mails | Easy | [▶ Practice](sql_sandbox.html?slug=find-users-with-valid-emails) |

